name: Simple 1500 Jitsuyou Series Vol. 09: Watashi Style no Aromatherapy
overview: Simple 1500 Jitsuyou Series Vol.09 - Watashi Style no Aromatherapy is the ninth game in the practical 1500 series released for the Playstation One console by D3 Publisher. This time the game features a complete glossary of aromatherapy, and the plaeyr answering some questions will know what aroma is the best one for him or her.
